🎬 Movie Preference Survey – Built with PyShiny
A simple and clean web-based movie survey app using PyShiny (Shiny for Python). Users can input their name, region, age, and income, rate a selection of movies, and leave open feedback.

This app is a beginner project aimed at learning how to build interactive apps using Shiny Express, Pandas, and basic form layout and styling with CSS.

✨ Features
User-friendly survey form

Responsive layout using cards and columns

Collects demographic data and movie preferences

Saves submissions to a local CSV file

Custom styling with CSS

🧰 Tools & Technologies
Python 3.10+

Shiny for Python

Shiny Express

Pandas

CSS (for styling)

